== Purpose ==

This template adds a loudspeaker icon to indicate audio.  Clicking the icon ''does not'' download the audio file.

== Usage ==

: <code><nowiki>{{spoken}}</nowiki></code>

gives this:
: {{spoken}}

== See also ==

* {{tl|Audio}}, a template meant for inline sounds with a link, like pronunciations (with clickable loudspeaker).
** {{tl|Audio-nohelp}}, a variant of this template with no help link.
* {{tl|Listen}}, which sets an audio clip off from the main text.

